<h1 class="title">In Memory of Fred Lo</h1>
<p class="description">In December 2016, we lost our father. We miss him everyday. He was the chairman of our board of directors, our biggest supporter and fan, and he was instrumental in the launch of Lo &amp; Sons. This is his story.</p>
