<h2 class="title">Love &amp; Family</h2>
<p class="description">While pursuing his Ph.D., our dad met our wonderful mother Helen, who was also pursuing her Ph.D. at Brandeis University. Soon they were married during a winter snowstorm in Woodstock, Vermont. But the warm weather of California was calling, and our mom and dad eventually moved west to Los Angeles where dad worked in astronomy at Caltech for about 12 years. And that’s where we were born!</p>
