<h2 class="title">A Scholar &amp; World Traveler</h2>
<p class="description">Professionally, he was an accomplished astronomer who discovered a black hole in the center of our galaxy. He was passionate about science, but he was also passionate about travel. And because the field of astronomy has a very international community, he was a seasoned globe trotter with over 5 million miles flown in his lifetime. Having walked once around the south pole, he is one of the few people in the world who can claim that they’ve walked around the world at least once. His life and our experiences with him are a big reason why we love to travel and why we ultimately created Lo &amp; Sons.</p>
